title_email_appointment_accepted: Hello {{re_name}}, your appointment has been accepted!
body_email_appointment_accepted: Dear {{re_name}}, the owner {{owner_name}} {{owner_surname}} has accepted the appointment on date {{appointment_date}} for your client {{client_name}} with identity document {{client_nif}} to visit the home {{ref}} in {{street}} with price {{price}}. The fees set at the time of acceptance of this appointment are {{agency_commissions}}% on the retail price with a minimum of € {{minimum_commission}} plus VAT. Serve this e-mail as proof of said appointment, but for the effective client registration, the appointment must be specified with a visit to the property and subsequent assessment of the owner. At that time a client registration document will be generated in your favor. Good luck on your visit. Immozon.

D. {{owner_name}} {{owner_surname}} verifies that on date {{date}} the real estate agency {{commercial_name}} has made a commercial visit with the client {{client_name}} with identity document {{client_dni}} to the next home object of the Sales order with the inmozon platform and its member real estate agencies:
  • {{street}}, {{city}}, {{county}}
  • {{price}}
  • Fees {{agency_commisions}} on pvp with a minimum of {{minimum_commission}} plus VAT
And for the record, electronically sign this. {{owner_name}} {{owner_surname}}
